trans-unit.source: Represents a static header item on a smart tag panel.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en statisk overskriftselementet på et smartkort koden panel.

trans-unit.source: Like the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionTextItem> base class, DesignerActionHeaderItem represents individual static text items in a smart tag panel.
trans-unit.target: Som den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionTextItem>basisklassen, DesignerActionHeaderItem representerer individuelle statisk tekstelementer i et smartkort koden panel.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionTextItem>

trans-unit.source: However, DesignerActionHeaderItem entries are displayed using bold text.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid vises DesignerActionHeaderItem oppføringene med fet tekst.

trans-unit.source: Typically, a header item is used to create a heading for a group of items in a panel.
trans-unit.target: En overskriftselementet brukes vanligvis til å opprette en overskrift for en gruppe elementer i et panel.

trans-unit.source: Clicking on a header item causes no action.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du klikker på en overskriftselementet gjør noe.

trans-unit.source: Individual panel items are associated together to form a panel by calling the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList.GetSortedActionItems%2A> method of the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> class.
trans-unit.target: Individuelle elementer som er knyttet til sammen for å danne et panel ved å kalle <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList.GetSortedActionItems%2A>metoden for <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>klasse.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList.GetSortedActionItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionHeaderItem"></xref> class using the provided name string.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionHeaderItem"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av angitte strengen.

trans-unit.source: This constructor sets both the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.DisplayName%2A> and the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Category%2A> properties to the value of the `displayName` parameter and sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Description%2A> property to `null`.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren angir både den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.DisplayName%2A>og <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Category%2A>Egenskaper med verdien for den `displayName` parameteren og angir de <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Description%2A>egenskapen `null`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Description%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Category%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.DisplayName%2A>

trans-unit.source: The text to be displayed in the header.
trans-unit.target: Teksten som skal vises i overskriften.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionHeaderItem"></xref> class using the provided name and category strings.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionHeaderItem"> </xref> klasse ved hjelp av de angitte navn og kategori strengene.

trans-unit.source: This constructor sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem.Description%2A> property to `null`.
The text to be displayed in the header.
trans-unit.target: Teksten som skal vises i overskriften.

trans-unit.source: The case-sensitive <xref:System.String> that defines the groupings of panel entries.
trans-unit.target: Den skiller <xref:System.String>som definerer grupperinger av panelet oppføringer.</xref:System.String>
